column1: # Name: Knowledge of HIV prevention methods, female, no education

# Definition: The percent of respondents who, in response to a prompted question, say that people can protect themselves from contracting HIV by using condoms or having sex only with one faithful, uninfected partner, by highest educational level of respondent
